myyuk.exam.stream

Class Stream<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • myyuk.exam.stream.Stream<T>

  • public class Stream<T>
extends Object
    Stream is inspired by other streaming engines. Users can registering producer, consumer (and others) to Stream instead of create threads directly.
